🔹 Q2) Write a cursor to update the income of all people living in ‘Urban’ area by 10%.


---

✅ Cursor

DO $$
DECLARE
    rec RECORD;
BEGIN
    FOR rec IN
        SELECT p.pnumber
        FROM person p
        JOIN area a ON p.aname = a.aname
        WHERE a.area_type = 'urban'
    LOOP
        UPDATE person
        SET income = income * 1.10
        WHERE pnumber = rec.pnumber;
    END LOOP;
END;
$$;


