🔁 OR

❓ Write a trigger before insert the record of person if the person number is negative raise the message “Invalid Number”.


---

✅ Trigger

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION check_pnumber()
RETURNS TRIGGER AS
$$
BEGIN
    IF NEW.pnumber < 0 THEN
        RAISE EXCEPTION 'Invalid Number';
    END IF;
    RETURN NEW;
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;

CREATE TRIGGER trg_person
BEFORE INSERT ON person
FOR EACH ROW
EXECUTE FUNCTION check_pnumber();


